				<pubDate>Sun, 02 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://entropydecrease.github.io/posts/just_and_nushell/</guid>
				<description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;justfile&#34;&gt;justfile&lt;a href=&#34;#justfile&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;几个相关的网站：&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;    href=&#34;https://just.systems/man/zh/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;https://just.systems/man/zh/&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;    href=&#34;https://github.com/casey/just&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;https://github.com/casey/just&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a&#xA;    href=&#34;https://quickref.cn/docs/justfile.html&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;https://quickref.cn/docs/justfile.html&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;是一个类似makefile的工具，但是更现代化，功能更强。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
